{"type":"article","id":7293,"title":"王美余慘死案涉中共非法人體器官買賣","uid":9304,"topics":[867],"contents":"王美余因强制摘取可移植人體器官死亡，并非毒打致死。匆匆火化，律師與家屬始終未見王美余遺體(采訪即可證實)。<br>\n<br>\n為回應國際社會壓力，中共中央廢除一直執行的强制摘取犯人可移植器官政策。默許地方强力部門與醫療機構不變。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EHs1WfaWwAAd8Oy?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EHs1WfaWwAAd8Oy?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EHs1WfaWwAAd8Oy?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EHs2QDvUwAA526o?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EHs2QDvUwAA526o?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EHs2QDvUwAA526o?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EHs2T4IVAAAeFgI?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EHs2T4IVAAAeFgI?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EHs2T4IVAAAeFgI?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2019-10-31","agreeCount":4,"discussionCount":0}